                     <additions>
                        <p>On <locus>f. 105<hi rend="superscript">v</hi></locus>, a manuscript note <q xml:lang="sa">|| śrī sarvavidhānadhānakavinrācaryasarasvatānāṃ śāvarabhāṣye 'dhamonavamaśvādhyāya ||</q> in black ink.</p>
                        <p>On <locus>f. 105<hi rend="superscript">v</hi></locus>, a manuscript note <q xml:lang="sa">|| śrī sarvavidhānidhāvakavinrācaryasarasvatīnāṃ śāvarabhāṣyenavamodhyāya ||</q> in black ink.</p>
                        <p>Abbreviation <q>bhā°a</q> written on the top left margin throughout the manuscript, above the original foliation.</p>
                        <p><q>Rāma</q> written on the bottom right margin throughout the manuscript, above the original foliation.</p>
                       <p>Occasional marginal and interlinear corrections in multiple hands, one of them being that of the scribe.</p>
